{"tid":1319382,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"公道自在人心 支持警察 餐廳8折優惠","createTime":"2019-07-15T06:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T13:21:24.000Z","uid":9471,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"70e9124c675805dfa5685dde6e5fb2eed0e1adb5","tid":1319382,"uid":9471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:54:01.000Z","msg":"一哥開到聲稱讚警察<span style=\"color: red;\">黑制</span>，阿蛇佢地企足成日，夜晚仲要<span style=\"color: red;\">大大力咁毆落去咁攰</span>，仲要<span style=\"color: red;\">小心收埋張證</span>又怕掉落黎俾人汁到，全港市民一定幫你地加油。<br />\n<br />\n呼籲全港餐廳，只要阿蛇叫餐前<span style=\"color: red;\">拎出警察委任證</span>及係餐廳<span style=\"color: red;\">高呼我係警察</span>，將得到全單8折優惠，以喂朥各位辛苦既克警<br />\n<br />\n餐廳內應會出現：<br />\n- 各食客大聲叫克制的警察好 加埋<span style=\"color: red;\">大大力既掌</span> 聲<br />\n- 食客排隊<span style=\"color: red;\">幫阿蛇影相</span>，放上IG呃like<br />\n- 同枱囡囡見阿蛇咁威應該<span style=\"color: red;\">濕晒</span>，阿蛇今晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿蛇唔洗怕羞，<span style=\"color: red;\">好人好者洗咩怕俾人知職業</span>，TVB話廣大市民支持你地架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n召喚開餐廳既巴打提供呢個優惠 或者 要求撐警餐廳提供呢個優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，撐警餐廳唔提供即係支持暴徒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c6ec22c9da136da8fbf82baf4ee0704f465fad","tid":1319382,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】有人冒警！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"80bc377bdfe677a743f94de327d9cd57003b3d2c","tid":1319382,"uid":276707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d16b4be2f701c1deb33fb21545983fee91a1e0","ti